es%20for%20people%20under%20age%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slew%20of%20actions%20comes%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20transgender%20people%20make%20up%20only%20a%20small%20minority%20of%20the%20US%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202024%20election%20campaign%20he%20repeatedly%20hammered%20Democrats%20on%20the%20divisive%20issue%20of%20transgender%20rights%20during%20the%202024%20election%20campaign%2C%20capitalizing%20on%20a%20broader%20culture%20war%20over%20the%20topic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Trump's%20most%20successful%20attack%20lines%20against%20his%20election%20rival%20Kamala%20Harris%20--%20%26quot%3BKamala%20Harris%20is%20for%20they%2Fthem.%20President%20Trump%20his%20for%20you%26quot%3B%20--%20targeted%20her%20support%20for%20trans%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20also%20targeted%20her%20one-time%20support%20for%20gender%20reassignment%20operations%20for%20prisoners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20executive%20order%20on%20Wednesday%20comes%20after%20the%20Republican-led%20House%20of%20Representatives%20in%20January%20passed%20a%20bill%20severely%20restricting%20transgender%20athletes%20from%20participating%20in%20girls'%20and%20women's%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20transgender%20people%20have%20become%20a%20more%20visible%20presence%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20sparking%20questions%20around%20gender%20norms%20and%20fairness%2C%20many%20conservatives%20have%20rallied%20around%20women's%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738809360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fr7bo1208_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_05_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-signs-order-banning-transgender-females-from-womens-sports-7644168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Don