20mindset%20to%20our%20travels.%20Sometimes%2C%20it's%20as%20simple%20as%20picking%20up%20trash%20on%20a%20beach.%20Other%20times%2C%20it's%20more%20involved%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolunteer-sustainable-travel-wwoofing-organic-farm-in-switzerland-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evolunteering%20at%20a%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20center%20in%20Seville%2C%20or%20harvesting%20grapes%20at%20a%20family-run%20winery%20in%20Croatia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20I'll%20admit%20we're%20far%20from%20perfect.%20Without%20external%20accountability%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20let%20good%20intentions%20take%20a%20backseat%20to%20the%20thrill%20of%20exploring%20new%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20stay%20grounded%2C%20we've%20adopted%20a%20schedule%3A%20once%20a%20week%2C%20we%20hold%20a%20%26quot%3Bbusiness%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20I%2C%20as%20CEO%2C%20focus%20on%20big-picture%20goals%2C%20while%20Nigel%2C%20as%20COO%2C%20digs%20into%20the%20details.%20We%20review%20finances%2C%20plan%20travel%2C%20and%20align%20on%20short-%20and%20long-term%20priorities.%20This%20rhythm%20provides%20structure%20and%20keeps%20us%20focused%20on%20creating%20impact%20while%20exploring%20new%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f5a5c04-6773-43d3-a2d3-e4a1137b1eb4%5C%22%3ELessons%20from%20the%20Champagne%20test%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20travels%20feel%20like%20an%20extended%20behavioral%20change%20initiative%2C%20only%20this%20time%2C%20I'm%20the%20client.%20The%20strategies%20I%20once%20taught%20others%20are%20now%20shaping%20my%20own%20experience.%20Leaving%20the%20corporate%20world%20meant%20stepping%20into%20an%20unstructured%20but%20not%20unexamined%20life.%20Retirement%20has%20been%20an%20exercise%20in%20reimagining%20value%20%E2%80%94%20both%20personal%20and%20global.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20journey%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20embrace%20imperfection.%20For%20someone%20who%20thrives%20on%20strategy%20and%20execution%2C%20not%20