C%20preferences%2C%20and%20activities%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20federal%20government.%20Trump%20also%20criticized%20DEI%20programs%20and%20diversity-related%20hiring%20goals%20at%20private%20companies%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail%20and%20since%20taking%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20set%20a%20goal%20in%202020%20to%20increase%20leadership%20representation%20of%20Black%2B%2C%20Latinx%2B%2C%20and%20Native%20American%2B%20employees%20by%2030%25.%20It%20reached%20that%20goal%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.googleusercontent.com%2Fmedia%2Fabout.google%2Fen%2F%2Fbelonging%2Fdiversity-annual-report%2F2024%2Fstatic%2Fpdfs%2Fgoogle_2024_diversity_annual_report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20company's%20annual%20diversity%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20decision%20to%20shift%20its%20hiring%20goals%20reflects%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20companies%20pulling%20back%20on%20DEI%20initiatives%2C%20beginning%20before%20Trump%20was%20reelected.%20Some%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20scaled%20back%20diversity%20efforts%20before%20his%20inauguration%20include%20Walmart%2C%20Ford%2C%20John%20Deere%2C%20Tractor%20Supply%20Company%2C%20and%20Lowe's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20also%20announced%20last%20month%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20have%20a%20team%20focused%20on%20DEI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-ends-dei-initiatives-memo-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETarget%20recently%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20will%20end%20multiple%20programs%20related%20to%20DEI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20companies%20have%20defended%20their%20DEI%20programs%20and%20policies%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcostco-shareholders-reject-anti-dei-proposal-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECostco%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20JPMorgan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20Google%20memo%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EWith%20new%20U.S.%20Executive%20Orders%2C%20court%20decisions%2C%20and%20many%20companies%20making%20changes%20to%20their%20DEl%20programs%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20we%20sat%20down%20with%20Fiona%20Cicconi%20to%20learn%20how%20Google%20is%20thinking%20about%20this.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20tell%20us%20how%20we're%20thinking%20about%20this%20across%20the%20company%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EFirst%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20clear%3A%20we've%20always%20been%20committed%20to%20creating%20a%20workplace%20where%20we%20hire%20the%20best%20people%20wherever%20we%20operate%2C%20create%20an%20environment%20where%20everyone%20can%20thrive%2C%20and%20treat%20everyone%20fairly.%20That's%20exactly%20what%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20going%20forward.%20Our%20users%20come%20from%20all%20across%20the%20US%20and%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20we%20serve%20them%20better%20when%20our%20employees%20do%2C%20too.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EEvery%20year%2C%20we%20review%20the%20programs%20designed%20to%20help%20us%20get%20there%20and%20make%20changes.%20And%20because%20we%20are%20a%20federal%20contractor%2C%20our%20teams%20are%20also%20evaluating%20changes%20to%20our%20programs%20required%20to%20comply%20with%20recent%20court%20decisions%20and%20U.S.%20Executive%20Orders%20on%20this%20topic.%20For%20example%2C%20in%202020%2C%20we%20set%20aspirational%20hiring%20goals%20and%20focused%20on%20growing%20our%20offices%20outside%20California%20and%20New%20York%20to%20improve%20representation.%20We'll%20continue%20to%20invest%20in%20states%20across%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20many%20countries%20globally%20%E2%80%94%20but%20in%20the%20future%20we%20will%20no%20longer%20have%20aspirational%20goals.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20mentioned%20we'll%20evaluate%20our%20programs.%20Can%20you%20share%20more%20about%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EMelonie%20Parker%20and%20her%20team%20will%20lead%20on%20closely%20and%20carefully%20evaluating%20programs%2C%20trainings%2C%20and%20initiatives%2C%20and%20will%20update%20them%20as%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20that%20raise%20risk%2C%20or%20that%20aren't%20as%20impactful%20as%20we'd%20hoped.%20She'll%20work%20with%20senior%20leaders%20across%20the%20company.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20is%20there%20anything%20else%20you%20want%20Googlers%20to%20know%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3EWhile%20there%20will%20be%20changes%2C%20our%20central%20Employee%20Resource%20Groups%20will%20remain%2C%20as%20will%20our%20work%20with%20colleges%20and%20universities%2C%20and%20our%20work%20to%20build%20products%20to%20help%20all%20our%20users%20and%20partners.%20That%20is%20all%20vital%20work%20for%20our%20business%20and%20our%20Googler%20community.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Google%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20from%20a%20non-work%20email%20and%20device%20at%20aaltchek%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ends-diversity-hiring-goals-reviews-dei-programs-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738799135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3cd56eb4be2fff9a3a672%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ends-diversity-hiring-goals-reviews-dei-programs-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20federal%20contractor%2C%20our%20teams%20are%20also%20evaluating%20changes%20required%20following%20recent%20court%20decisions%20and%20executive%20orders.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek%2CHugh%20Langley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A162%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ends-di