0interested%20in%20science%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20apply%20the%20scientific%20method%20or%20scientific%20inquiry%20to%20everyday%20life.%20We'll%20often%20talk%20about%20things%20like%20the%20yeast%20in%20our%20sourdough%20starter%20or%20how%20to%20measure%20liquids%20properly%20in%20a%20measuring%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20favorite%20summer%20activities%20is%20gardening%3B%20he%20and%20my%20husband%20will%20plant%20a%20small%20assortment%20of%20vegetables%2C%20and%20he%20is%20thrilled%20to%20help%20care%20for%20and%20eat%20them.%20We%20discuss%20what%20the%20plants%20need%20to%20grow%20and%20how%20bees%20help%20pollinate%20certain%20plants.%20We%20even%20planted%20some%20tickle-me%20plants%20indoors%20%E2%80%94%20their%20leaves%20close%20up%20when%20they're%20touched%2C%20which%20is%20a%20defense%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObserving%20nature%20can%20be%20an%20experiment%20of%20itself%3B%20watching%20the%20raindrops%2C%20seeing%20how%20high%20the%20water%20splashes%20when%20jumping%20versus%20stepping%20in%20puddles%2C%20or%20watching%20the%20leaves%20turn%20colors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20winter%2C%20we've%20learned%20about%20simple%20reactions%20by%20doing%20experiments%20with%20everyday%20household%20items%2C%20such%20as%20mixing%20baking%20soda%20and%20vinegar%20in%20a%20zip-top%20plastic%20bag%20that%20has%20been%20decorated%20with%20a%20snowman%20face.%20The%20baking%20soda%20and%20vinegar%20react%20to%20form%20carbon%20dioxide%2C%20which%20builds%20up%20when%20the%20bag%20is%20sealed%2C%20causing%20the%20bag%20to%20expand%20until%20it%20pops%2C%20causing%20an%20exploding%20snowman!%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20zip-top%20bag%20filled%20with%20a%20mixture%20of%20vinegar%20and%20baking%20soda%20that%20was%20used%20for%20a%20child's%20science%20experiment.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3dc36eb4be2fff9a3ad19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20winter%2C%20my%20son%20enjoyed%20making%20exploding%20snowmen%20using%20a%20zip-top%20bag%20and%20a%20mixture%20of%20vinegar%20and%20baking%20soda.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3EFor%20another%20fun%20activity%2C%20we%20use%20salt%20as%20snow%20melt%20and%20pretend%20to%20go%20%26quot%3Bice%20fishing%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20cereal%20bowl%20full%20of%20water%20and%20ice.%20Putting%20salt%20on%20an%20ice%20cube%20changes%20the%20freezing%20point%2C%20causing%20the%20ice%20to%20melt%20faster.%20Placing%20a%20string%20on%20the%20ice%20cube%20can%20emulate%20ice%20fishing%2C%20as%20the%20ice%20cube%20will%20refreeze%20over%20the%20string%20once%20the%20salt%20becomes%20diluted%20by%20the%20surrounding%20water.%20I%20have%20to%20admit%2C%20it's%20pretty%20fun%20to%20watch%20my%20kids%20swing%20the%20ice%20cubes%20around!%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20hands%20of%20two%20children%20are%20near%20a%20green%20bowl%20filled%20with%20water%20and%20ice%20as%20the%20children%20learn%20about%20how%20salt%20impacts%20melting%20point.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3dd92bfebcc4d029df1e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20of%20my%20kids%20enjoy%20this%20ice%20fishing%20experiment%20that%20shows%20how%20salt%20can%20impact%20the%20freezing%20point%20of%20ice.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0306ee3-a1a7-41d3-b230-2cdd92ab4e85%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20turn%20bath%20time%20into%20a%20fun%20experiment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%20son's%20Christmas%20stocking%20was%20stuffed%20with%20a%20few%20bath%20potions%20that%20have%20been%20a%20big%20hit.%20He%20has%20both%20powder%20and%20mini%20bath%20bomb%20cubes%20that%20fit%20inside%20of%20a%20flask.%20You%20pour%20warm%20water%20into%20the%20flask%20and%20it%20reacts%20to%20form%20a%20colorful%20mini%20volcano.%20My%20son%20took%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20pour%20some%20of%20the%20potion%20into%20another%20flask%20or%20take%20the%20cubes%20out.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe've%20reused%20the%20flask%20with%20bath%20color%20tablets%20and%20it%20resulted%20in%20a%20similar%20reaction%20(albeit%20smaller).%20He%20has%20fun%20playing%20pretend%20with%20the%20potions%2C%20often%20imitating%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fwhere-to-watch-bluey-stream-online%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBluey%20minisode%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BStrong%20Potion%2C%26quot%3B%20asking%20me%20to%20buy%20his%20potions%20and%20choosing%20what%20animal%20they'll%20turn%20me%20into%2C%20similar%20to%20what%20happens%20in%20the%20cartoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22809c938a-685d-4448-9841-e84e980cfcfa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20embrace%20science%20and%20building%20kits%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20participate%20in%20activities%20outside%20of%20our%20home%2C%20such%20as%20the%20(free!)%20Lowe's%20and%20Home%20Depot%20kids'%20DIY%20workshops%2C%20where%20kids%20build%20things%20like%20toy%20snowplows%20and%20snowflake%20ornaments.%20Sharing%20these%20moments%20with%20my%20kids%20reminds%20me%20of%20my%20own%20youth.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20dad%20often%20built%20science%20kits%20with%20me%20when%20I%20was%20a%20child.%20I%20especially%20remember%20a%20build-a-radio%20kit%20and%20taking%20apart%20a%20broken%20VCR%20player%2C%20just%20to%20see%20what%20it%20looked%20like%20inside.%20They%20were%20precious%20bonding%20moments%2C%20but%20also%20sparked%20a%20sense%20of%20curiosity%20in%20my%20young%20mind.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20might%20have%20wanted%20to%20be%20the%20president%20or%20an%20actress%2C%20but%20these%20projects%20taught%20me%20important%20life%20skill%20sets%20that%20led%20me%20to%20a%20career%20in%20science.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20doing%20the%20same%20with%20my%20children.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMy%20son%20was%20given%20a%20science%20kit%20last%20year%20for%20his%20birthday%20and%20we've%20been%20working%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F8-awesomely-simple-science-experiments-you-can-do-at-home-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiment%20list%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20is%20especially%20enamored%20with%20the%20book%20%3Cem%3EHow%20Things%20Work%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20he%20was%20gifted%20after%20multiple%20library%20checkouts.%20It%20has%20experiments%20and%20games%20in%20it%2C%20but%20also%20stories%20and%20his%20favorite%20%E2%80%94%20a%20page%20that%20shows%20all%20of%20the%20lines%20(internet%2C%20water%2C%20sewer)%20going%20throughout%20a%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-science-stem-fun-young-kids-tips-from-scientist-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738797481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a231297bb3f854015ba732%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-science-stem-fun-young-kids-tips-from-scientist-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20lab%20technician%2C%20I'm%20doing%20these%20four%20things%20%E2%80%94%20including%20turning%20bath%20time%20into%20a%20fun%20experiment%20%E2%80%94%20to%20get%20my%20young%20children%20excited%20about%20science.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Anne%20James)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaking-science-stem-fun-young-kids-tips-from-scientist-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NBA%3A%20Golden%20State%20Warriors%20eye%20Pelicans%20star%20if%20the%20Kevin%20Durant%20deal%20falls%20through%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publis