milar%20sellers%20like%20Shein%20isn't%20exactly%20clear%2C%20but%20let's%20just%20assume%20it's%3Cem%3E%20not%20good%3C%2Fem%3E.%20(Temu%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20both%20e-commerce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-wont-be-killed-by-de-minimis-exemption-changes-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplatforms%20have%20advanced%20beyond%20only%20shipping%20direct%20from%20mainland%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20now%20many%20of%20their%20sellers%20have%20warehouses%20in%20the%20US%20to%20ship%20orders%20domestically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20homepage%20of%20Temu%2C%20the%20top%20promoted%20section%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Blocal%20warehouse%20stores%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20sellers%20from%20warehouses%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22temu%20app%20site%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3c3afbfebcc4d029de7d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22726%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BLocal%20warehouse%20stores%26quot%3B%20on%20Temu%20ship%20from%20within%20the%20U.S.%3Cp%3ETemu%20%2F%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShein's%20website%20has%20a%20less%20prominent%20tab%20for%20%26quot%3BQuickShip%26quot%3B%20items%20that%20ship%20from%20the%20US%2C%20which%20isn't%20visible%20at%20all%20on%20its%20mobile%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20relations%20with%20one%20of%20our%20largest%20trade%20partners%20are%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%20I%20have%20great%20news%20about%20my%20mousepad%20(which%20I'm%20sure%20you%20were%20worried%20about).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Temu%20order%20appears%20to%20be%20still%20moving%20along%20in%20processing%20to%20be%20shipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-shein-china-shipping-trump-my-order-tariff-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738791836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a3d477bfebcc4d029dee03%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-shein-china-shipping-trump-my-order-tariff-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Trump's%20order%20ending%20the%20%26quot%3Bde%20minimis%26quot%3B%20exception%20and%20the%20USPS%20at%20least%20temporarily%20halting%20packages%20from%20China%2C%20what%20about%20my%20Temu%20package%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-shein-china-shipping-trump-my-order-tariff-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20closed%20a%20China%20loophole.%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20were%20already%20prepared.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20the%20Shein%20Activation%20at%20the%20Shein%20VIP%20party%20during%20Parklife%20Festival%20at%20Heaton%20Park%20on%20June%208%2C%202024%20in%20Manchester%2C%20England.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674f8329ef9a5d904789c758%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Shein%20Activation%20in%20Manchester%2C%20England.%3Cp%3EAnthony%20Devlin%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Shein%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump's%20executive%20order%20ending%20de%20minimis%20shipments%20hurts%20Shein%20and%20Temu.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20companies%20have%20prepared%20for%20changes%20by%20fulfilling%20more%20orders%20locally%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExperts%20say%20Shein%20and%20Temu's%20success%20relies%20on%20low%20prices%2C%20not%20de%20minimis%20shipments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShein%20and%20Temu%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewon't%20meet%20an%20untimely%20end%20because%20of%20de%20minimis%20changes%2C%20e-commerce%20experts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20logistics%20world%20has%20been%20expecting%20changes%20to%20the%20de%20minimis%20exemption%20for%20a%20while%2C%20and%20both%20Chinese%20e-commerce%20players%20have%20made%20some%20changes%20to%20their%20fulfillment%20strategies%20that%20experts%20say%20could%20help%20cushion%20the%20blow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemu%20and%20Shein%20disrupted%20the%20e-commerce%20industry%20in%20part%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-de-minimis-tax-loophole-scrutiny-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavoiding%20paying%20duty%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20shipments%20through%20a%20provision%20of%20customs%20law%20called%20Section%20321%2C%20also%20known%20as%20de%20minimis.%20These%20shipments%20came%20on%20planes%20directly%20from%20China%20and%20were%20able%20to%20make%20use%20of%20the%20Section%20321%20provision%20because%20they%20were%20valued%20at%20less%20than%20%24800%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbrands-scramble-as-trump-ends-de-minimis-shipments-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20executive%20order%20Trump%20issued%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20February%201%20effectively%20closes%20that%20loophole%20for%20goods%20originating%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20certainly%20have%20an%20impact%2C%20but%20it's%20much%20smaller%20than%20people%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20Alex%20Yancher%2C%20CEO%20of%20Passport%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20helps%20brands%20sell%20globally%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dfd6a4b7-05f5-48d1-a67f-2aee70691112%5C%22%3EGoing%20local%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShein%20and%20Temu%20have%20mainly%20prepared%20for%20de%20minimis%20disruption%20by%20having%20more%20orders%20fulfilled%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20majority%20of%20its%20orders%20were%20still%20coming%20on%20planes%20from%20China%2C%20Shein%20started%20fulfilling%20more%20of%20them%20from%20US%20warehouses%20in%202022%20and%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fretail-consumer%2Fshein-shifts-shipping-strategy-bring-china-made-goods-closer-us-shoppers-2023-09-22%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20from%20ImportGenius%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Reuters%20reported.%20Shein%20opened%20its%20first%20US-based%20warehouse%20in%20Whitestown%2C%20Indiana%2C%20in%202022%2C%20and%20in%202024%20it%20opened%20an%20office%20in%20Bellevue%2C%20Washington%2C%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20hub%20for%20its%20US%20fulfillment%20and%20logistics%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETemu%20also%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-opens-its-marketplace-to-us-based-sellers-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowing%20US-based%20vendors%20to%20sell%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20marketplace%20in%202024.%20This%20newer%20model%20allowed%20sellers%20with%20warehouses%20in%20the%20US%20to%20handle%20fulfillment%20and%20logistics%20themselves%2C%20creating%20orders%20that%20would%20not%20need%20to%20cross%20borders%20before%20making%20their%20way%20to%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProducts%20from%20those%20vendors%20are%20designated%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Blocal%26quot%3B%20badge%20on%20their%20listing%20page%20and%20in%20search%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d9cc443-327d-4eae-83f7-827668130891%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20'RIP%20Temu%20and%20RIP%20Shein%2C'%20experts%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFulfilling%20orders%20locally%20in%20the%20US%20is%20a%20departure%20from%20how%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20started%20out.%20But%20e-commerce%20experts%20say%20it%20doesn't%20disrupt%20the%20main%20drivers%20of%20their%20success%3A%20ultra-low%20prices%20and%20very%20trendy%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShein%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20a%20unique%20model%20in%20which%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-to-sell-supply-chain-technology-experts-debate-challenges-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartners%20directly%20with%20manufacturers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20create%20small%20batches%20of%20only%20the%20most%20in-demand%20items.%20That%20model%20has%20allowed%20it%20to%20test%20consumer%20appetite%20and%20turn%20around%20clothing%20designs%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShein's%20manufacturing%20model%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20what%20has%20made%20the%20company%20successful%2C%20not%20its%20reliance%20on%20de%20minimis%20shipments%2C%20said%20Kirthi%20Kalyanam%2C%20a%20professor%20and%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Retail%20Management%20Institute%20at%20the%20Leavey%20School%20of%20Business%20at%20Santa%20Clara%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20de%20minimis%20shipping%20has%20been%20at%20least%20tightened%20up%20or%20turned%20off%2C%20I%20expect%20whatever%20price%20advantage%20they%20have%20due%20to%20the%20de%20minimis%20shipping%20to%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalyanam%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20that%20their%20other%20capabilities%20are%20going%20to%20go%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJuozas%20Kaziuk%C4%97nas%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20e-commerce%20intelligence%20firm%20Marketplace%20Pulse%2C%20echoed%20that%20sentiment%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20keep%20seeing%20'RIP%20Temu%20and%20RIP%20Shein'%20everywhere%20because%20of%20de%20minimis%20changes%2C%20but%20while%20de%20minimis%20helped%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20to%20get%20here%2C%20it%20disappearing%20won't%20be%20the%20end%20of%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Shein%20and%20Temu%20did%20not%20return%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Both%20companies%20have%20previously%20said%20that%20they%20do%20not%20rely%20on%20de%20minimis%20to%20grow%20their%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20customers%20could%20see%20higher%20prices%20and%20longer%20shipping%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDe%20minimis%20clearance%20was%20very%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20almost%20an%20electronic%20data%20exchange%20that%20theoretically%20costs%20between%20five%20and%2010%20cents%20per%20shipment%2C%26quot%3B%20Derek%20Lossing%2C%20founder%20of%20supply%20chain%20advisory%20firm%20Cirrus%20Global%20Advisors%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20a%20more%20formal%20clearance%20now%20required%2C%20that%20will%20add%20friction%20to%20the%20process%2C%20and%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbp.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fnational-media-release%2Fcbp-proposes-new-rule-strengthen-enforcement-and-limit-duty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20de%20minimis%20shipments%20increased%20by%20more%20than%20600%25%20between%202015%20and%202023%2C%20going%20from%20139%20million%20a%20year%20to%20more%20than%201%20billion.%20More%20than%201.36%20billion%20shipments%20were%20sent%20via%20de%20minimis%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20CBP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20logistics%20world%20has%20been%20expecting%20change%20for%20some%20time%2C%20many%20were%20surprised%20by%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20it%20went%20into%20effect.%20In%20lieu%20of%20several%20months%20to%20adjust%20their%20supply%20chain%20operations%20to%20comply%20with%20any%20potential%20policy%20changes%2C%20they%20had%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20trade%20situation%20continues%20to%20evolve%20quickly.%20The%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20have%20been%20put%20on%20pause%2C%20while%20those%20on%20Chinese-made%20goods%20have%20gone%20ahead.%20On%20Tuesday%20evening%2C%20the%20United%20States%20Postal%20Service%20said%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fusps-pause-accepting-packages-from-china-hong-kong-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20accept%20p