e%20conflict%20began%20when%20the%20US%20imposed%20a%2010%25%20tariff%20on%20all%20Chinese%20goods%2C%20prompting%20China%20to%20retaliate%20with%20tariffs%20ranging%20from%2010%25%20to%2015%25%20on%20certain%20US%20products%2C%20including%20coal%2C%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%2C%20crude%20oil%2C%20agricultural%20machinery%2C%20and%20large-displacement%20cars.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnChina's%20countermeasures%2C%20set%20to%20take%20effect%20on%20Monday%2C%20also%20include%20adding%20two%20American%20companies%2C%20Illumina%20and%20PVH%20Group%2C%20owner%20of%20Calvin%20Klein%20and%20Tommy%20Hilfiger%2C%20to%20its%20unreliable%20entities%20list.%20This%20move%20severely%20limits%20the%20companies'%20ability%20to%20operate%20in%20China%2C%20citing%20violations%20of%20normal%20market%20trading%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20remains%20uncertain%2C%20with%20some%20experts%20speculating%20that%20the%20two%20nations%20may%20agree%20to%20postpone%20further%20action%20to%20engage%20in%20dialogue.%20Clark%20Packard%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Cato%20Institute's%20Herbert%20A.%20Stiefel%20Center%20for%20Trade%20Policy%20Studies%2C%20warned%20that%20if%20a%20deal%20isn't%20reached%2C%20the%20conflict%20could%20escalate%20rapidly%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F02%2F05%2Feconomy%2Ftariffs-trade-war-with-china%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIf%20a%20similar%20deal%20isn't%20reached%2C%20then%20I%20think%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20fairly%20intense%2C%26quot%3B%20Packard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20imposed%20by%20the%20US%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20for%20American%20consumers%2C%20affecting%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20goods%2C%20including%20consumer%20electronics%2C%20toys%2C%20and%20apparel.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20increased%20costs%20of%20importing%20raw%20materials%2C%20such%20as%20rubber%2C%20plastic%2C%20and%20chemicals%2C%20could%20negatively%20impact%20American%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20may%20also%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%2C%20including%20job%20losses%20in%20both%20China%20and%20the%20US.%20Morgan%20Stanley%20economists%20predict%20that%20the%20US%20will%20impose%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20China%20later%20this%20year%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20further%20retaliation%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20potentially%20more%20devastating%20scenario%20is%20a%20three-way%20trade%20war%20involving%20the%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20other%20nations%2C%20such%20as%20Mexico%20and%20Canada.%20Citibank%20economists%20warn%20that%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20significant%20economic%20contraction%20in%20the%20US%2C%20with%20the%20economy%20predicted%20to%20shrink%20by%200.8%25%20this%20year%20and%20-1.1%25%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina's%20economy%20would%20be%20impacted%20less%20this%20year%20and%20next%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20US%2C%20despite%20heavy%20tariffs%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20economies%20of%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20will%20be%20hit%20majorly%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738777140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fr7bo1208_donald-trump-reuters_625x300_05_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-a-three-way-trade-war-with-china-mexico-and-canada-could-weaken-the-us-7643284%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20economy%20would%20be%20impacted%20less%20this%20year%20and%20next%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20US%2C%20despite%20heavy%20tariffs%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20economies%20of%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20will%20be%20hit%20majorly%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GST%20authorities%20cla