-because-colombian-president-petro-proposes-cocaine-legalization%2Famp_articleshow%2F117955103.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Was%20Nair%20Not%20Picked%20For%20CT%202025%3F%20Gill%20Says%20'He's%20Great%20But%20Doesn't..%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Karun%20Nair%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1708-karun-nair-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKarun%20Nair%3C%2Fa%3E%20turned%20the%20heads%20of%20one%20and%20all%20during%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%202024%2F25%2C%20slamming%20a%20stunning%20779%20runs%20in%20eight%20innings%2C%20including%20five%20centuries.%20The%2033-year-old's%20astonishing%20performances%20for%20Vidarbha%20even%20raised%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20he%20should%20be%20selected%20as%20a%20wildcard%20in%20India's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20squad.%20However%2C%20the%20impressive%20form%20ended%20up%20coming%20too%20late%2C%20as%20he%20failed%20to%20make%20the%20cut%20for%20the%2015-man%20squad.%20India%20vice-captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shubman%20Gill%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108578-shubman-gill-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShubman%20Gill%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20his%20two%20cents%20on%20Karun%20Nair's%20non-selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGill%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20continuity%20to%20ensure%20a%20secure%20team%20environment%20rather%20than%20making%20frequent%20changes%20based%20on%20domestic%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarun%20had%20a%20great%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20the%20current%20players%20should%20be%20dropped.%20They%20have%20also%20performed%20well%20to%20reach%20this%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lost%20only%20one%20game%20in%20the%20World%20Cups.%20The%20players%20in%20the%20squad%20have%20contributed%20significantly%2C%20and%20while%20it's%20unfortunate%20for%20those%20excelling%20in%20domestic%20cricket%20who%20weren't%20picked%2C%20constant%20ch